<br>
Also with the new pet agro changes there is no reason to worry about your pet causing agro as you run through a zone.  However there are still pathing issues that will make you need to be sure your warder is with you at all times.  Otherwise he might get stuck and lost.  Zonning will, as long as you warder still alive, bring your warder to your side unbuffed at the new zone line.<br>
<br>
