<br>
To "unsummon" your pet, it is now the consensus that the pet commands are working across the zone.  So you should be able to type "/pet get lost" from anywhere, and the pet should leave you.<br>
<br>
Secondly, about the pet zoning with you, yes, it will.  You can leave your pet parked anywhere in the zone, and when you zone, he'll come out at your side when you finish zoning. <p><p>
